Angela Ahrendts , CEO of Burberry and the author of this month's  How I Did It , spoke with HBR contributing editor Karen Dillon at an event in London. She discussed how the storied fashion brand uses social media to connect its employees and outside stakeholders: She also emphasized the importance of emotional intelligence in business. 